  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he is going to be in a bunker together with these other boys in mobellager.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when she goes to work, her group was passing by there, it was arranged with the kapo that on the way back from work, she would join her son in the bunker and spend the night with them.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then in the morning, she would be picked up by her group again to go to work, so nobody would notice that she's not at work.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] At that time, we had an idea or at least-- this is what it seems to me-- that the boys had some problems joining a group of partisans.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was the-- the Polish underground was divided.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was the mainstream, the Home Army, the Armia Krajowa; there was the left, the Armia Ludowa, the False Army; and there were some very right-wing group, some of them extremely virulent and very, very anti-Semitic who actually fought-- fought with the Germans and with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the idea was that they may have some problems finding the-- the AL, which is the Volksarmee that did accept Jews.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I didn't know, and I still don't know exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the next thing I knew, on the 18th of March, I came back from work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the night when my mother was supposed to-- to be-- to join my brother.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
